00:10:32.600 --> 00:10:34.560
Terimakasih tuan!

00:10:35.600 --> 00:10:37.680
Disini!  O-Di sini!

00:10:41.760 --> 00:10:43.920
'Dan kamu harus bergegas.
Saatnya bagi perempuan

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:46.160
