Uruvi!

00:12:39.960 --> 00:12:41.000
Uruvi!

00:13:03.960 --> 00:13:04.880
Uruvi..

00:13:12.480 --> 00:13:13.400
Uruvi.

00:13:49.760 --> 00:13:51.040
Tolong berhenti di situ.

00:13:52.600 --> 00:13:54.480
Silakan datang ke sini
setelah beberapa waktu.

00:14:01.200 --> 00:14:03.160
Istri saya belum selesai mandi.

00:14:56.840 --> 00:14:58.360 line:20%
